        <P><FONT FACE="Times New Roman" SIZE="-1">Dear Client:</FONT></P>
        <P><FONT FACE="Times New Roman" SIZE="-1"> D.S. Sewing, Inc., a maker of fine custom 
            tarpaulins, banner blanks, wind screens, swimming pool covers, field 
            covers, and other sewn industrial products, carries an extensive 
            line of vinyl laminates, vinyl coated polyesters, and 
            polypropylenes. We continually secure bargains on quality material 
            and pass the savings along to our customers. </FONT></P>
        <P><FONT FACE="Times New Roman" SIZE="-1">We will be glad to quote you a price based on 
            your product specifications or accommodate any needs you may have 
            for an industrial sewn product. As a manufacturer of quality 
            industrial sewn products, we can custom sew tarps of any style or 
            size to cover your company's needs. </FONT></P>
        <P><FONT FACE="Times New Roman" SIZE="-1">Our products are custom designed and fabricated 
            for durability, easy handling, and strength. Our ongoing 
            relationships with national fabric vendors guarantee you the highest 
            quality material at the lowest possible price. Whether it's a 
            trailer, pool, or field needing protection, we'll produce a quality 
            cover meeting your high standards. </FONT></P>
        <P><FONT FACE="Times New Roman" SIZE="-1">We look forward to becoming your preferred 
            source for our quality products, and to thank you for your continued 
            business or to welcome you aboard as a new client.
          </FONT></P>
